<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>404 — Page Not Found | 3M Studio</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            background: #0b0f19;
            color: #f3f4f6;
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 5rem;
            color: #8b5cf6;
            margin: 0;
            font-weight: 800;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #9ca3af;
            margin: 10px 0 30px;
            max-width: 450px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        a {
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border: 1px solid #8b5cf6;
            background: #8b5cf6;
            padding: 12px 28px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
        }
        a:hover {
            background: transparent;
            color: #8b5cf6;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>404</h1>
    <p>We couldn't find the page you are looking for. It might have been moved or deleted.</p>
    <a href="/">Return Home</a>
</body>
</html>
